Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.39,0:01:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手，Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.05,0:01:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好跟她道歉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.32,0:01:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有妳在，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是攻擊聲納的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#23 巨人的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣我感到很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過請你安靜的旁觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算叫個\N能幹的律師來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要避免秘銀與美軍對立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能做到這件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是一頭\N忘記怎麼游泳的鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOY BOX，轉向北方前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速至30節
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離2海浬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號跟4號的發射管口打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的，是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一雪我方所受的屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember Pearl Harbor\N(永遠記得珍珠港)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3號發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水中方位2-9-8\N偵測到高速螺旋槳聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推定是某種魚雷一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝向本艦接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況太惡劣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻把潛艦交給我掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有釋放操舵員跟聲納員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可是事關這艘潛艦\N是否會沉沒的緊要關頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都不知道能不能躲得掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是絕對做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不試試看怎麼會知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想自殺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是世界最豪華的自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有數十億美金的船陪葬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不討厭這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是他那種\N有勇無謀的恐怖行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意成為俘虜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是向邦克山號發射飛彈等行為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從一開始就看錯這個男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，就來場測膽賽跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛航至深度1500
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告，這項命令會超過耐壓深度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去\N我們會一起變成鯊魚的餌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說這艘船\N不是游得比魚雷還快嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的魚雷可是快得不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對手還是美軍耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要虛張聲勢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起雙手出來投降吧，克魯茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我救你也可以喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起到指揮中心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟九龍說一聲\N然後殺一個船員給他看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就能正式\N成為我們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酬勞也不少喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好遜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丟臉死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好了，克魯茲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘銀是傭兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼正義使者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是被人用錢雇用的殺人集團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往錢出得比較多的顧客那邊靠攏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我們的常識，不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算耍帥，重視什麼義理人情的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點好處也沒有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了，關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把你解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再向泰莎要求獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要她讓我拍穿泳裝的性感照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一張20美金的價錢\N賣給艦內的傢伙們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100人買的話就有2000美金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你是更聰明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼聰明不聰明的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是比較現實罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(無艦長或副艦長允許 禁止進入)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥，鑰匙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAROS？\N(傳輸回饋整合球艙)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像比\N Arbalest(強弩兵)的TAROS還要舊型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連結的不是入-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是這艘潛艦的控制系統
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隱隱約約的理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，相良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊已經沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著可以過來救我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊，關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種錢簡直就是紙屑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來擦屁股都嫌難用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅會得痔瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會塞住馬桶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯茲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肉搏戰的天份，真是差勁透了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下撲過去，一下又逃開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像個小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會對克魯茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊，妳剛才在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.77,0:09:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在醫務室醒來後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到避難訓練的警報響得很大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想穿這副模樣到庫房去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就躲了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就看到這邊開始打起架來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩姬她也真是的\N不知道給我打了什麼奇怪的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全搞不清楚狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Venom(猛毒)怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭好昏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有照相機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三甲板B走道發生火災
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C系統第16號送水管破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.79,0:10:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一甲板H7的壓力阻壁\N發出異常聲響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了，來了，來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Al，轉右滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便散佈誘餌機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，要躲了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲得掉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，可能躲不掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的暗號\N發射1號、2號攔截飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用深海模式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，長官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是緊急爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，緊急爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說它躲掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，似乎是使用了緊急爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正朝向海面緊急浮起中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會在那種距離
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，究竟是什麼樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是有著鐵打的睪丸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是驚人的膽識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳用了什麼魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就代表\NDanann並不是很信賴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船已經是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你姿意妄為了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個女孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也會保護這艘船的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用腦袋想想吧，甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.47,0:13:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良中士，開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先來解開我們的手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一枚魚雷射過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得馬上控制住潛艦才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位2-7-8有一枚先進戰力魚雷\N(ADCAP:Advanced Capability)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離50
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰莎告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說不用擔心Danann
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中…中士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是魚雷的安全裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近有美軍的水上艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對方的潛艦把魚雷設定成\N不能越過某個深度以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免誤射到友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校預測到會有第二枚魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才用緊…緊急爆炸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龍，你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒打中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們在一開始就預測到\N我們這邊有安全裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除魚雷的安全裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再發射一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1號、2號的發射管注水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袋中之鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在正被逼至絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，他卻在享受這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打從內心，興奮的期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9局下半，兩出局滿壘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在腦裡只想著\N要把球打出場外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Venom(猛毒)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在正朝著球場走去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷的人快回到崗位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.67,0:16:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再檢查一次固定鋼索，動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傷患
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.54,0:16:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把擔架拿來，擔架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口待會再包紮就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先確保呼吸道的順暢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候才更要保持冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥德貝麗醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定裝載的貨物很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也要他們徹底遵守規定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是指揮中心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.74,0:17:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好您平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個恐怖份子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙控制了Al
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是多虧艦長，讓Danann恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖份子現在怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還躲在某處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在正打算用廣播警告…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛達特，那個恐怖份子受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，被相良中士開槍擊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是左肩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架紅色的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著傷患離開庫房
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還可以動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是相良中士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟能把Tuatha De Danann\N逼到如此的窘境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回故鄉去吧，宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只小要\N你連我們都想一起保護嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真高興啊，卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九龍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了你

